167
00:05:19,650 --> 00:05:23,233
[SPEAKER_06]: There are three principles that I intend to follow as I guide this council.

168
00:05:23,733 --> 00:05:25,575
[SPEAKER_06]: Collaboration, planning, and trust.

169
00:05:26,476 --> 00:05:34,162
