170
00:05:34,943 --> 00:05:42,689
[SPEAKER_06]: Later tonight, I'll present two items that will help organize us towards those principles, a new committee structure, and a governing agenda framework for our 2024-2025 term.

171
00:05:45,251 --> 00:05:51,873
[SPEAKER_06]: I know these will help the council collaborate better, plan better, and build trust across city government and with residents.

172
00:05:52,633 --> 00:05:55,014
[SPEAKER_06]: Nothing can get done in city government without collaboration.

173
00:05:55,754 --> 00:06:09,838
