182
00:07:16,847 --> 00:07:24,471
[SPEAKER_06]: I'm glad that some of that plan has been incorporated into the budget ordinance discussions that we've had and initial meetings to set up the financial task force.

183
00:07:25,558 --> 00:07:37,463
